data.title: Battle of the Network Stars (2017)
data.meta_description: The revival of the 1970-80s celebrity athletic competition is hosted by Mike Greenberg and Joe Tessitore with NFL's DeMarcus Ware and Ronda Rousey as team captains with current television stars and classic celebrities who participated in the original series.
